commit_message: Remove source code and indicate code is legacy.  Note, git allows one to go back in history to retrieve the old code, for those who want that.
Skip VCF records with blank variant sequences.  Could be caused by an unexpected upstream flow alignment.

Will check if both BAM and .bai files are present at the begining, before execution of the python script, and if execution of external process like python script failed.  Will check PATH for location of SamToFlowgramAlign.jar and samRegionOverlap.py if executable called without path.
Fix to so that :cannot-merge is actually displayed as a note, not a warning.
Remove ending ; from INFO field of VCF.  Set version to non-beta.
Added some info about running under CentOS 5.6
Refactored code changing to use more proper names, like Flowgram Alignment, and FlowAlignRecord

Allows python-bin and samtools-bin to specify binary without path, if it is in the they can be found in some path inside PATH env

Allows python-bin and samtools-bin to specify binary without path, if it is in the they can be found in some path inside PATH env
Added contig information to vcf header by reading in BAM header using samtools.

Various adjustments to output to remove most messages from vcf-validator.
Change CANNOT-MERGE warning to a note.
Refactored vcf tag into classes. Added some missing tags.  Better display of main command called.
Bayesian_Score tag placement, allows for greater number of variant reads (old limit of 90000)
Changes to the VCF output format, adding headers and genotype column.  Also added flag --vcf-tag-format that can control this.
Update docs
Remove compile time warnings about *vh-version*
Made consist versioning for program. Currently v. 0.1.3alpha.
Change to error output when java completes.  Corrected Usage statement in help.
Updated README file.
README added that describes why we modified the stock sbcl.

Fix to particular read which caused the score calculation to get a NIL value.  Specifically, argument X is not a NUMBER: NIL error in CALC-ENDS-OF-READ-FACTOR method called by CALC-DEVIATION-SCORE. Issue TS-2644.
Fixed file open bug where stdin and stderr streams of external python process were not being closed.  Issue TS-2608.
Remove some compile warning, changed scoring for 1bp deletion which may impact when alternative SNPs are present, increase buffer size.
Added script used in Torrent Server downstream of variant hunter.
Merge branch 'master' of https://github.com/iontorrent/Ion-Variant-Hunter
Added util scripts for debugging and a README for the directory
Adjusted build.xml so that it would work with older ant
Make build.xml work with older ants (no nested file name in move.
Added a couple informational files, have single LICENSE file, and lib directory that won't be under source control.
main-class in build.xml points to the correct place
Updated README, changed build.xml to copy .py script dist.
Changing directory structure.  Adding required helper python script for ion-variant-hunter-core.
Added license information
* initial commit
